question.string: Which Secretary of State was significantly involved in the United States' dominance of the Caribbean?
question.pseudoquery: PREFIX text:<http://jena.apache.org/text#> SELECT DISTINCT ?proj WHERE { ?proj text:query (<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/abstract> '"Secretary of State"' 1000). ?proj ?pbridge <http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States>. } LIMIT 12

question.string: Which German mathematicians were members of the von Braun rocket group?
question.pseudoquery: PREFIX text:<http://jena.apache.org/text#> SELECT DISTINCT ?proj WHERE { ?const text:query (<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/abstract> '"rocket group"' 1000). ?const <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/populationPlace> ?proj. } LIMIT 12

question.string: Which movie by the Coen brothers stars John Turturro in the role of a New York City playwright?
question.pseudoquery: PREFIX text:<http://jena.apache.org/text#> SELECT DISTINCT ?proj WHERE { ?proj text:query (<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/abstract> '"New York City" AND "Coen brothers stars"' 1000). ?proj a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Film>. } LIMIT 1
